Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.94,0:00:48.98,PS1,NTP,0,0,0,,要上發條嗎  不上發條嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.40,0:00:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要上發條嗎  不上發條嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:05.20,PS1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}要上發條嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.56,0:02:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我從學校回來就看到這個放在門口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是寄給純的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,純終於也和正常人一樣開始對女孩子感興趣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:07.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要給爸爸媽媽發短信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.18,0:03:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做工很精良啊  軟軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.76,0:03:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然穿著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:49.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發條？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然一見面就伸手亂摸淑女的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.94,0:04:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,時代竟然已經進步到了這個程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名字？  櫻田純
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個不美麗的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,薔薇少女的第五人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(539,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:53.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而純  你今後就是我真紅的僕人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,僕人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙到底被設定了些什麼對話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:05:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  親吻那只戒指吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拔不下來……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰要親啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就給我沏紅茶來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:11.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,紅茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要用95℃以上溫度的熱水沖泡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.52,0:05:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然後加上熱牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.64,0:05:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼我要做這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給你  這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,溫度太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:36.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,茶葉沒泡開  香氣也散逸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.65,0:05:38.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這根本不能叫紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久違
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,58萬6920小時又37分沒見了呢  真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,薔薇少女的第一人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.31,0:06:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(541,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:15.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,七位薔薇少女都醒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(601,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.67,0:06:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲遊戲開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.34,0:06:25.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲遊戲  又要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,純  快親吻戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.69,0:06:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:51.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是挑釁在先哦  水銀燈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能放出人工精靈來就比較麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  梅梅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(702,656)}Meimei
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要嘛  人家害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再會吧  真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  真紅  剛才那是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,薔薇少女人偶共有七位
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(518,656)}Rozen Maiden
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.21,0:07:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是七姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是將原本獨一無二的薔薇聖母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs-2\pos(882,656)}Rosa Mystica
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,分成七個碎片製作出的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:28.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每人只是七分之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.59,0:07:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必須把七分之一的碎片恢復到一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.57,0:07:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們要互相爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了孕育父親夢中的少女愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雛梅  別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不哭  所以你要快點回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
