Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:08:59.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想你啊  真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:21.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  這個人類是無害的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的僕人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰是僕人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那她也是那個薔薇什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是薔薇少女的第三人偶
